---
title: Coley Massaman Curry with Limey Jasmine Rice
description: This recipe mixes sweet, fragrant spices, creamy coconut milk and the salty, savoury taste of peanut butter for the perfect Thai-inspired massaman curry. Our chefs have used coley as its flavour and texture (which is often compared to cod) are great with such intense flavour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/coley-massaman-curry-3fa8e2a0-bc1cba55.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/coley-massaman-curry-5dc40975622f8a38f5146a49-39258edf.pdf
